Constructor:-
Special method invoked automatically at time of objects creation.
used for Initialisation:-
1.same name as class
2.Constructor doesn,t have a return type
3.Only called once(automatically), at object creation
4.Memory allocation happens when Constructor is called



//ise  public me declared karte hai


Constructor ek special function hai jo class ka object create hote hi automatically call hota hai.
Iska kaam hota hai: object ki initial value set karna.